{
  "stem": "5261.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have seen in there two or three-- this is in German-- [GERMAN], toilet [GERMAN], toilet [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because you see, in the room, you have eaten, eaten.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] And there was piss, there was the toilet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If somebody had this diarrhea, he couldn't use it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because in this cell, it was like mafia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The one boss, the one highest person and his clan, he had the rules of these cells.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had time for pissing, for using only morning, not evening, for taking the food, if we could.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because usually when the door was open, where the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is the name of the prisoners who brought the food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Let's say morning, they have small piece of bread, some margarine-- not every day, every second or Saturday-- and one spoon of marmalade, probably.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now I know, because this marmalade was so thin, like soup.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Probably in the kitchen prison, steal something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[SPEAKING NON-ENGLISH] also, they put water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The marmalade, it was so thin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But even this thin marmalade, I never tried.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There, from mafia, the boss, he gave the top, and I have to give to this [NON-ENGLISH] put it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I give him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were standing in the queue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the next one, and everybody has to give the spoon of marmalade to, for him, so that he had.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It happened the same with the margarine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And in this cell, when I arrived, I never forget.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Maybe I can change-- I can mention now this name.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Maybe this family is still alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was Apfelbaum.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He was much older than me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He, he had a David star.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He has seen that I was so young, shy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He asked me in Polish, what for?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, I told to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It so stupid way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe later I will explain.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
